  <thing id="raCBOMXISV" name="Secret of the Vault Seed" description="\nMythic xiomorns possess an innate understanding of {i}Vault Seeds{/i} - the magic-rich artifacts that grow into the xiomorns&apos; underground vaults. This process includes finding the raw crystals the seeds are formed from on the Plane of Earth, faceting the gem and using magic to grow it into its shape, and nurturing the seed with the proper spells once it&apos;s planted in the raw earth from which the Vault will grow.\n\nA mythic xiomorn gains regeneration 10 while in a Vault it created or directly helped create. No attack form causes this regeneration to stop functioning; a mythic xiomorn can be killed by hit point damage only if removed from its Vault first." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Mythic xiomorns possess an innate understanding of Vault Seeds">
